channel.title: I got CLR
channel.description:
I picked up Introduction to Algorithms by Cormen, Leiserson, and Rivest.
It does a good job of explaining how common data structures and algorithms are implemented.
Also, i'd probably have to get it for university anyway, so now I have it for that.
Discuss CLR or other computer science books.
